{"type":"message","id":"f65b5cf9","parentId":"fb162a8d","timestamp":"2026-03-27T20:53:58.469Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The only session is the cron job itself. This cron job is running right now, and there's no other user conversation in the last 5 minutes. The sessions_list shows only one session which is this cron job. So there are no active user conversations.\n\nLet me execute the autonomous learning task. I need to:\n1. Search for latest news on enterprise digital transformation, smart security, network system integration, IT operations services\n2. Organize 3-5 key pieces of information\n3. Save to /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md\n\nLet me search for industry trends first.","thinkingSignature":"5ab0b5d7d7e7fc439a69d923cc11cce633f02857e08efa740a00ba394db2d59d"},{"type":"text","text":"当前仅有本 cron 任务活跃，无用户对话。开始执行自主学习。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_2g4it0tncfb3_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":643,"output":186,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44810,"cost":{"input":0.0001929,"output":0.00022319999999999998,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0017355299999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774644832970}}
{"type":"message","id":"240fda38","parentId":"f65b5cf9","timestamp":"2026-03-27T20:53:58.475Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_2g4it0tncfb3_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774644838472}}
{"type":"message","id":"83934eac","parentId":"240fda38","timestamp":"2026-03-27T20:54:02.961Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me search for the latest industry trends in enterprise digital transformation, smart security, network system integration, and IT operations services.","thinkingSignature":"55f929f532779df032aa64c6c54b0e0676a060f8009e0d8f32059e6b6d4d093a"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9mqtqt9ci9ke_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型 2026 最新政策趋势\" --output text 2>/dev/null | head -100","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9mqtqt9ci9ke_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防行业 2026 最新动态 技术趋势\" --output text 2>/dev/null | head -100","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9mqtqt9ci9ke_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"网络系统集成 IT运维服务 2026 行业发展动态\" --output text 2>/dev/null | head -100","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1344,"output":217,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45542,"cost":{"input":0.0004032,"output":0.0002604,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0019830299999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774644838475}}
